Program: Great Lives
Title: Pope John Paul II
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00gj64w
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 30 Jan 2007
Ann Widdicombe is famous for her opposition to women priests, so it is no surprise to find that she has chosen someone who felt just as strongly on the matter, the last Pope, John Paul II. Malachi O'Doherty, author, and presenter Matthew Parris join in the debate.